Il concept:
	il giocatore é un elfo, della casa Tulje, perso in una gigantesca caverna.
	gli elfi adorano Veon
	deve trovare la strada per ritornare a Kelmera, la sua casa => per fare questo deve attraversare 
		la caverna
	la società elfica é divisa in più casati, spesso in lotta tra di loro
		SPUNTO: altri elfi che vagano e attaccano il pg ?
	gli yuan-ti sono nemici degli elfi
		spunto: gli yuan-ti si muovono più velocemente in acqua o vicino all'acqua, hanno scurovisione
	ci sono funghi per nutrirsi ( e curarsi )
		al posto delle pozioni curative
	alcuni enormi funghi emettono luce e cristalli
		SPUNTO: rendono visibile sempre alle altre creature i loro dintorni
		SPUNTO: giocatore può raccogliore i cristalli per avere una luce che poi riesce a droppare?
	
		 
	 









--------------------------------------IDEAS BELOW-
player can attack from distance using f. then move to select target
an enemy that attack you from distance, use line
drop item from quickslots, press d and number to drop
add scroll of darkness: put some space in full darkness for X turn. Creature(even player) cannot see anything
add poisoned mouse: on attack a small chance to get player poisoned, for 15 turns lose 1 hp
add crate item: open, find another random item
a static enemy that cures everything in range (5 squares), "Health spores"
a static enemy that poison everything in range (5 squares), "Poison square"
dungeon generation traits
	- low light: half player radius
	- normal light: normal player radius
	- monster madness: +50% monsters
	- unpotion: no potions available



add gravedigger with following behaviour: wander, search for dead body, avoid contact with player

add stamina to every creature. With stamina 0 creature must stop and wait. 
	Stamina regenerate 10 stamina for turn
	Player have on start 40 stamina
add items to enhance stamina (fungus)
add abilities. Each of them have a cost in stamina see (). Abilities are in three tiers:
	tier 1: basic ability, enhance creature attack, senses, etc..
	tier 2: advanced ability,  do something creature cannot do
	tier 3: change reality
	TIER 1:
		attack (1): default ability for every creature
		dash (20): move of 5 tiles in any perperdicular direction, stop if anything on line
		hide into darkness (40): creature become invisible to everyone for 10 turns, if attacks
			exit from invisibility
		100 senses (40): enhance vision radius of double for 5 turns
	TIER 2:
		story of blades (40): attack in any tile around every enemy
		invulnerability (40): creature become invulnerable for 10 turns, cannot move or attack
		
	TIER 3:
		mirror images (40): creature create duplicate of itself (fake creatures with 1 hp, no special
			abilities) that behave like creature
		turn stone to dust (80): creature turn stone into dust, destroy wall on touch for 10 turns

